{"tid":1078164,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"越簡單嘅餸 越難整得好 例如蒸滑蛋","createTime":"2019-03-26T06:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T02:07:23.000Z","uid":221265,"like":3,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5d60c09f06b8aaae4535732d08c543ae9a3fccf3","tid":1078164,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T06:07:15.000Z","msg":"今次1人分量<br />\n1隻雞🥚蛋1隻鹹蛋<br />\n蛋槳+水（暖水）比例1:1.5<br />\n效果不錯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來大家俾個<span style=\"color: red;\">蒸</span>字fake咗<br />\n蒸只需要大火40-45秒<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">焗</span>先係關鍵<br />\n蒸完要焗佢10分鐘，咁就冇豆皮冇嚡口亦唔會水汪汪未熟。<br />\n<br />\n我第一次蒸，仲蒸得好過老母。<br />\n<br />\n不過要留意，蛋黃事前要蒸佢2分鐘先；亦可以成個鹹蛋煲佢3-4分鐘之後剝殻（我今次就係雞蛋+鹹蛋白撈成蛋漿，蛋黃拿去蒸）。當然加皮蛋也ok,但皮蛋最好剝殻先蒸佢2分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n你哋有冇其他秘㊙️技？或master到啲難整得好嘅家常簡單餸？歡迎分享。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tGBW9Dd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtGBW9Dd.png&h=d5faa31b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知實有人屌芫茜/蔥，不過個人喜好，你當然可以唔落。鹹蛋亦夠味，我唔會落豉油。"},{"pid":"58cad31a6eb5f0a2226347c70ada8bd34a2a886f","tid":1078164,"uid":105795,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T06:10:56.000Z","msg":"負皮是比芫茜/蔥的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n識食一定喺乜都唔落 加水加鹽原汁原味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fabad7b49c4af12c62cff0d29c613a994bd1ef68","tid":1078164,"uid":95637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T06:10:56.000Z","msg":"鹹蛋蒸水蛋好食咩 未試過"},{"pid":"8514d09d3ff15a1e1921e948c26e962199ac0cad","tid":1078164,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T06:11:00.000Z","msg":"包張保鮮紙一齊蒸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1e938e8df9d861914c13274725f6263fe18ec25","tid":1078164,"uid":16676,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid